Class FileSaver

java.lang.Object
utils.FileSaver
All Implemented Interfaces:
IFileSaver
public class FileSaver extends Object implements IFileSaver
FileSaver is a class responsible for saving various types of data (e.g., applicants, officers, managers, projects, enquiries, and applications) into their respective CSV files. This class supports writing to both default file paths and user-specified paths.
